This script written for Greek studends (ages 12-16).
Point is:
1. First try of Slackware Linux installation.(format disks gdisk,create root passwd,edit files in /etc, setup user account, groups etc..)
2. First try to install a linux.iso in QEMU using terminal.(what is the terminal use and power)
3. To play (edit) with the script and customise it at home.(create their own simple script no matter if its running properly but learn how to use shellcheck)

